/*+- Function ---------------------------------------------------------------+
  |         Name: _ftPushWin()          Docs: Keith A. Wire                  |
  |  Description: Push a new window on the screen                            |
  |       Author: Keith A. Wire                                              |
  | Date created: 10-03-93              Date updated:  10-03-93              |
